{"tid":2105084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(初選)最後一個鐘你應該做咩","createTime":"2020-07-12T11:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T12:21:29.000Z","uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"71c620e5ea0d24c78c7d32a73eb80ef06a28a94f","tid":2105084,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"你支持温和民主派？ok<br />\n你支持抗爭本士派？ok<br />\n但係你昵刻應該做咩？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>人數</strong><br />\n<br />\n無論你支持咩光譜，只要人數夠多，我地所選擇嘅人就會有高認受性，所以呢一刻你要做咩？就係不停問人「你投左初選未?」只要你說服多一個人投初選，我地所選嘅人就多一分認受性。所以，求下各位唔好再討論其他野，試下問人、食完飯拉屋企人去散步唔小心去左票站再順便投埋票，試下去唔去到60萬<br />\n<br />\n利申:半個鐘r左廿個"},{"pid":"790bac6f59a004295a6e01d26fca6ac0641764cd","tid":2105084,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:42:48.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"37be145d2b56dd036e2378845d379ddfeb9efcc6","tid":2105084,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:43:09.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"ff683f57ccad6b643d3359fb31f53dedb66b8838","tid":2105084,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:43:45.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"79d0c0385f67cbee8179e5aebdba7f25805a5660","tid":2105084,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"9267575b50a9889d0144f16615bb56490b0a6103","tid":2105084,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:44:52.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"02e6bbd5c8f0def389a805906708edad592d0926","tid":2105084,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:45:16.000Z","msg":"推5/10"},{"pid":"07d48a5a4ea7f2136898f1b1344b1efaeb38d8f6","tid":2105084,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:45:48.000Z","msg":"推6/10"},{"pid":"926c7002fcc2733591e3593a7854b6469cbfe02c","tid":2105084,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:46:0